attachments.title: Stop Worrying About the New Google Maps; These URL Parameters Are Gold
attachments.text: Somewhat inspired by a Pete Wailes YouMoz post from many years ago, I set out last week to explore Google Maps with a fresh set of eyes and an open mind to see what I could discover about how it renders local business results. Read on, for what I think I found.
